org.opencypher.gremlin.translation.translator

Class Translator<T,P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opencypher.gremlin.translation.translator.Translator<T,P>

  • public final class Translator<T,P>
extends Object
    Abstraction over the process of building a translation for different targets.

    Translator instances are not reusable.
